class="gs_ri"><h3 class="gs_rt"><span class="gs_ctc"><span class="gs_ct1">[HTML]</span><span class="gs_ct2">[HTML]</span></span> <a   href="http://msb.embopress.org/content/5/1/262.abstract" data-clk="hl=en&amp;sa=T&amp;oi=ggp&amp;ct=res&amp;cd=20&amp;ei=57f3V_-OOca_mAGdoIjwAw">The impact of cellular networks on disease comorbidity</a></h3><div class="gs_a">J Park, <a href="/citations?user=9WByIioAAAAJ&amp;hl=en&amp;oi=sra">DS Lee</a>, <a href="/citations?user=sR_OzkgAAAAJ&amp;hl=en&amp;oi=sra">NA Christakis</a>&hellip; - Molecular systems  &hellip;, 2009 -
